{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Remove all pro-fossil fuel advertising and replace with climate crisis facts.",
        "additional_details": "Some companies use the side of their oil and petrochemical tankers to promote the use of shale gas on the basis of prosperity and future fuels. This is promoting destruction of the planet and encouraging the climate crisis. \r\nAs a climate crisis has been declared, this kind of advertising should be banned.",
        "background": "Much in the same way that cigarette companies cannot advertise due to the health risks associated, and have also been made to show images of the impact of smoking on a person, fossil fuel companies should be made to show images of the impact they are having on the planet and the global population.",
